        "markdown_formatted": "## Meeting Purpose\n\n[Reconnect on Ataccama's LLM visibility needs.](https://fathom.video/share/X-4Z5Wqt29XRQVoFfNyZjjZfCENyURjY?tab=summary&timestamp=141.0)\n\n## Key Takeaways\n\n  - [**Problem:** Ataccama's organic web traffic has dropped \\~25% in the last quarter, a decline that persists post-holidays.](https://fathom.video/share/X-4Z5Wqt29XRQVoFfNyZjjZfCENyURjY?tab=summary&timestamp=177.0)\n  - [**Hypothesis:** Users are shifting research to LLMs (e.g., ChatGPT), where competitors like Informatica and Collibra have superior visibility.](https://fathom.video/share/X-4Z5Wqt29XRQVoFfNyZjjZfCENyURjY?tab=summary&timestamp=177.0)\n  - [**Need:** A solution to analyze LLM ranking and provide an action plan to improve positioning.](https://fathom.video/share/X-4Z5Wqt29XRQVoFfNyZjjZfCENyURjY?tab=summary&timestamp=227.0)\n  - [**Next Step:** A meeting next week with VP of Growth Marketing Sophie Rares to evaluate growthx.ai's end-to-end service, which includes strategy, content creation, and monitoring.](https://fathom.video/share/X-4Z5Wqt29XRQVoFfNyZjjZfCENyURjY?tab=summary&timestamp=428.0)\n\n## Topics\n\n### Ataccama's Challenge: Declining Organic Traffic\n\n  - [Organic web traffic has dropped \\~25% in the last quarter, a decline that persists post-holidays.](https://fathom.video/share/X-4Z5Wqt29XRQVoFfNyZjjZfCENyURjY?tab=summary&timestamp=177.0)\n  - [This has caused a \"crazy\" drop in monthly active users.](https://fathom.video/share/X-4Z5Wqt29XRQVoFfNyZjjZfCENyURjY?tab=summary&timestamp=284.0)\n  - [**Hypothesis:** Users are shifting research to LLMs (e.g., ChatGPT, Claude), where competitors like Informatica and Collibra have superior visibility.](https://fathom.video/share/X-4Z5Wqt29XRQVoFfNyZjjZfCENyURjY?tab=summary&timestamp=177.0)\n  - [**Identified Gaps:**](https://fathom.video/share/X-4Z5Wqt29XRQVoFfNyZjjZfCENyURjY?tab=summary&timestamp=212.0)\n      - [Weaker backlinking than competitors.](https://fathom.video/share/X-4Z5Wqt29XRQVoFfNyZjjZfCENyURjY?tab=summary&timestamp=212.0)\n      - [No Reddit presence, a key data source for LLMs.](https://fathom.video/share/X-4Z5Wqt29XRQVoFfNyZjjZfCENyURjY?tab=summary&timestamp=212.0)\n\n### Ataccama's Current Tooling & Evaluation\n\n  - [Ataccama uses **Scrunch** for basic LLM ranking analysis.](https://fathom.video/share/X-4Z5Wqt29XRQVoFfNyZjjZfCENyURjY?tab=summary&timestamp=158.0)\n  - [The current evaluation is for a tool to analyze LLM ranking and provide an action plan to improve positioning.](https://fathom.video/share/X-4Z5Wqt29XRQVoFfNyZjjZfCENyURjY?tab=summary&timestamp=388.0)\n  - [**Context:** George Samaras (Marketing Ops) is facilitating the intro; the primary decision-maker is Sophie Rares (VP of Growth Marketing).](https://fathom.video/share/X-4Z5Wqt29XRQVoFfNyZjjZfCENyURjY?tab=summary&timestamp=471.0)\n\n### growthx.ai's Proposed Solution\n\n  - [growthx.ai offers an end-to-end service combining agency partnership with a technology platform.](https://fathom.video/share/X-4Z5Wqt29XRQVoFfNyZjjZfCENyURjY?tab=summary&timestamp=449.0)\n  - [**Core Service:** Strategy, monitoring, and content creation (5 articles/week, new or refreshed) to improve LLM visibility and drive high-intent traffic.](https://fathom.video/share/X-4Z5Wqt29XRQVoFfNyZjjZfCENyURjY?tab=summary&timestamp=244.0)\n  - [**Deliverables:** A 6-month content roadmap and weekly/bi-weekly performance reports.](https://fathom.video/share/X-4Z5Wqt29XRQVoFfNyZjjZfCENyURjY?tab=summary&timestamp=351.0)\n  - [**Positioning:** A \"best of both worlds\" model (agency + tech) that differentiates from a pure technology tool like Scrunch.](https://fathom.video/share/X-4Z5Wqt29XRQVoFfNyZjjZfCENyURjY?tab=summary&timestamp=449.0)\n\n## Next Steps\n\n  - [**Tyler:** Prepare for the meeting next week with Sophie Rares (VP of Growth Marketing) to present growthx.ai's end-to-end service.](https://fathom.video/share/X-4Z5Wqt29XRQVoFfNyZjjZfCENyURjY?tab=summary&timestamp=428.0)\n  - [**George